  <brief_title>Identification of Markers (Klotho-FGF23 Axis) as Determinant in the Evolution of Arterial Stiffness During the First Year of Renal Transplant</brief_title>
  <acronym>KLOTHO</acronym>
  <official_title>Identification of Markers (Klotho-FGF23 Axis) as Determinant in the Evolution of Arterial Stiffness During the First Year of Renal Transplant</official_title>
  <sponsors>
